urmurs, rubs or gallops\nABD: Soft, non-tender, non-distended, No HSM.\nEXT: Good pulses, No clubbing, cyanosis or edema\n\nIMPRESSION: \nPatient has had a partial response to neoadjuvant chemotherapy for triple negative infiltrating ductal carcinoma of the right breast.\n","mentions":[{"begin":1762,"end":1768,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_323","classUri":"Breast","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":90},{"begin":509,"end":528,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_249","classUri":"AxillaryLymphNode","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":100},{"begin":1267,"end":1277,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_287","classUri":"MetastaticLesion","negated":true,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":100},{"begin":645,"end":649,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_257","classUri":"Mass","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":60},{"begin":1151,"end":1156,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_279","classUri":"Right","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":80},{"begin":1015,"end":1021,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_275","classUri":"Breast","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":90},{"begin":825,"end":835,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_267","classUri":"Doxorubicin","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":100},{"begin":339,"end":341,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_239","classUri":"M0StageFinding","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":80},{"begin":386,"end":392,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_243","classUri":"Breast","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":false,"confidence":90},{"begin":1140,"end":1150,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_278","classUri":"Metastatic","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":true,"confidence":100},{"begin":773,"end":793,"id":"fake_patient1_07072025191757_M_264","classUri":"AxillaryLymphNode","negated":false,"uncertain":false,"historic":t